item.title: Can some1 give me a PKbox? :D
item.dc:creator: @croranger croranger
item.description:
@croranger wrote:

search for this public void makeGlobalObject

under it you should see makeGlobalObject(xCOORD, yCOORD, ITEMID, 0, 10);//NAME

now keep adding this makeGlobalObject(xCOORD, yCOORD, ITEMID, 0, 10);//NAME

EXAMPLE:

makeGlobalObject(xCOORD, yCOORD, ITEMID, 0, 10);//NAME makeGlobalObject(xCOORD, yCOORD, ITEMID, 0, 10);//NAME makeGlobalObject(xCOORD, yCOORD, ITEMID, 0, 10);//NAME makeGlobalObject(xCOORD, yCOORD, ITEMID, 0, 10);//NAME makeGlobalObject(xCOORD, yCOORD, ITEMID, 0, 10);//NAME

  • change coordinates and item ids and you should be done.
